# NeuralRetail - Amdox Internship Project

Retail Analytics Platform using Machine Learning and Business Intelligence.

## Team
Group 6

## Modules
- Data Cleaning & Feature Engineering
- Demand Forecasting
- Customer Segmentation
- Churn Prediction
- Inventory Optimization
- Interactive Dashboard

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-Learn
- XGBoost
- Streamlit
- Plotly

## Dataset
Online Retail II Dataset
